    https://github.com/ultralytics/ultralytics/blob/main/LICENSE

Because these projects are themselves AGPL-3.0, any user who installs
the `[cv]` extra and then operates a modified version of OpenConstructionERP
over a network is subject to AGPL-3.0 obligations both from
OpenConstructionERP and independently from those upstream projects.
Commercial users who require a non-AGPL path for the computer-vision
takeoff pipeline must obtain commercial licences directly from Artifex
Software (PyMuPDF) and Ultralytics Inc. (YOLO) -- OpenConstructionERP's
commercial licence covers only OpenConstructionERP itself.

Users who install OpenConstructionERP without the `[cv]` extra do not
pull in these AGPL upstream packages.

